1
00:00:20,291 --> 00:00:22,125
[MASTER] And this building
where you find yourself

2
00:00:22,208 --> 00:00:24,125
is known as Tenjin-ya.

3
00:00:24,208 --> 00:00:26,416
Now why won't you
just give in and agree

4
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:27,625
to be my bride?

5
00:00:27,708 --> 00:00:29,250
I'll stay and work
till it's paid--

6
00:00:29,333 --> 00:00:32,083
that settles the debt,
but I won't have to marry you.

7
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:34,833
How would you like to
open your own restaurant here?

8
00:00:34,916 --> 00:00:36,875
My name is Matsuba.

9
00:00:36,958 --> 00:00:38,875
Master Matsuba.

10
00:00:38,958 --> 00:00:40,958
You're a great cook.

11
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:43,416
And so, sweet Aoi.

12
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:46,125
I would like you
to take this gift.

13
00:00:46,916 --> 00:00:49,541
[MASTER] It's not going to be
an easy task.

14
00:00:49,625 --> 00:00:52,083
A human has never run
a restaurant for <i>ayakashi</i>

15
00:00:52,166 --> 00:00:53,708
in the hidden realm before.

16
00:00:56,583 --> 00:01:00,125
Very well, then.
You can give it a try.

17
00:02:39,625 --> 00:02:42,208
[MYSTERIOUS AYAKASHI]
What do you wish me to do?

18
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:50,791
