19
00:02:50,875 --> 00:02:52,166
[MYSTERIOUS AYAKASHI]
Aoi.

20
00:02:52,250 --> 00:02:55,250
[gasps, giggles]

21
00:02:55,333 --> 00:02:58,166
[MYSTERIOUS AYAKASHI] Do you
have another wish, perhaps?

22
00:02:59,916 --> 00:03:02,875
I'm very hungry,

23
00:03:02,958 --> 00:03:06,750
and all I want
is my mom's curry and rice.

24
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:10,541
[MYSTERIOUS AYAKASHI]
This wish is difficult to grant.

25
00:03:10,625 --> 00:03:11,958
But...

26
00:03:45,958 --> 00:03:47,000
[AOI]
Gorgeous!

27
00:03:47,083 --> 00:03:48,416
I didn't know
the Hidden Realm

28
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:50,291
had this much nature!

29
00:03:51,375 --> 00:03:54,125
Yes, we have a variety
of environments here.

30
00:03:54,208 --> 00:03:55,750
It must be big.

31
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:58,375
Tenjin-ya is located
at the Northeast end.

32
00:03:58,458 --> 00:03:59,666
It's called the, "Ogre gate."

33
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:01,458
I see.

34
00:04:01,541 --> 00:04:02,875
[MASTER]
The capital is surrounded

35
00:04:02,958 --> 00:04:04,708
by eight lands
called the Hachiyo,

36
00:04:04,791 --> 00:04:06,083
or "eight leaves."

37
00:04:06,166 --> 00:04:08,166
The <i>ayakashi</i> who rule
each of these lands

38
00:04:08,250 --> 00:04:10,208
also carry the title of Hachiyo.

39
00:04:10,291 --> 00:04:12,125
Is Master Matsuba one of those?

40
00:04:12,208 --> 00:04:14,916
Indeed, he rules
the land called Mt. Shumon.

41
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,125
Wow.

42
00:04:16,208 --> 00:04:18,541
You did a great job
with Master Matsuba.

43
00:04:18,625 --> 00:04:21,666
Your cooking protected
Tenjin-ya from great dishonor,

44
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:23,750
and for that,
you deserve a reward.

45
00:04:23,833 --> 00:04:24,916
I do?

46
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,375
[UME, TAKE, MATSU]
Yeah, come on, Miss Aoi!

47
00:04:26,458 --> 00:04:28,583
Ah! You scared me,
don't sneak up!

48
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:31,875
[MATSU]
Let us do your hair!

49
00:04:31,958 --> 00:04:33,833
[TAKE]
Let us do your face, too!

50
00:04:33,916 --> 00:04:36,291
[UME]
Let us get you dressed up!

51
00:04:36,375 --> 00:04:38,583
[AOI] Whoa. I gotta say,
I wouldn't have

