lovely on you.

68
00:05:19,125 --> 00:05:22,208
I'm delighted to see
you like it, too, Aoi.

69
00:05:22,291 --> 00:05:25,541
Um, yeah, I do like it.
It's so beautiful.

70
00:05:26,458 --> 00:05:28,166
Thanks so much.

71
00:05:29,333 --> 00:05:30,916
Now, final touch.

72
00:05:37,458 --> 00:05:40,125
My, you wear it
incredibly well.

73
00:05:40,208 --> 00:05:43,375
Wait. Doesn't the bud
seem bigger to you?

74
00:05:43,458 --> 00:05:44,916
[MASTER]
It's made of rose quartz,

75
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,166
but it's enchanted to grow
like a real flower.

76
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:49,750
Soon, it will become
a full camellia blossom.

77
00:05:49,833 --> 00:05:51,500
You mean it's gonna bloom?

78
00:05:51,583 --> 00:05:54,833
Yes, and fall off one day,
just like a real flower.

79
00:05:54,916 --> 00:05:56,375
[AOI]
What? It'll fall?

80
00:05:56,458 --> 00:05:59,416
But, no then it's not gonna
be pretty anymore.

81
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,666
[MASTER chuckles]

82
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,833
[Aoi grumbles]

83
00:06:01,916 --> 00:06:03,625
You must pay
your grandfather's debt

84
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:05,416
before the bloom falls
from its setting.

85
00:06:05,500 --> 00:06:06,833
Now, you have your deadline.

86
00:06:06,916 --> 00:06:07,833
Good luck.

87
00:06:07,916 --> 00:06:08,916
[AOI grumbles]

88
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,500
[ATTENDANTS laugh]

89
00:06:10,583 --> 00:06:12,791
Come, we're expected
to arrive soon.

90
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:14,250
Where to?

91
00:06:23,166 --> 00:06:26,541
[AOI] It's unbelievable!
What is this place?

92
00:06:26,625 --> 00:06:28,833
[MASTER] This is the capital
of the hidden realm.

93
00:06:28,916 --> 00:06:30,083
It's called Youto.

94
00:06:30,166 --> 00:06:31,500
Youto?

95
00:06:31,583 --> 00:06:34,250
Right. It translates to,
" <i>ayakashi</i> capital."

96
00:06:34,333 --> 00:06:36,500
The <i>ayakashi</i> king resides here.

97
00:06:36,583 --> 00:06:38,333
[gasps]

98
00:06:38,416 --> 00:06:39,666
Heh!

99
00:06:50,166 --> 00:06:52,458
[MAN 3A] Look! Tenjin-ya's
Master Innkeeper!

100
00:06:52,541 --> 00:06:55,958
[MAN 3B] Such a fine ogre,
if I do say so!

101
00:06:56,041 --> 00:06:58,083
You're famous here,
aren't you?

102
00:06:58,166 --> 00:07:00,666
I am, but listen, Aoi.

103
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,458
You must keep your mask on,

104
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:04,833
or they'll know you're human
and you'll be in danger.

105
00:07:04,916 --> 00:07:06,500
Yeah, duh, I know that.

106
00:07:11,375 --> 00:07:14,208
[AOI] It seems like
there's a festival going on.

107
00:07:32,041 --> 00:07:33,958
[MASTER]
It's called Youto cut glass.

108
00:07:34,041 --> 00:07:35,708
That name does make sense.

109
