It's made using
a technique

110
00:07:37,416 --> 00:07:38,541
from the apparent realm,

111
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:40,958
but we modified it,
so our method's unique.

112
00:07:41,041 --> 00:07:43,250
Ah, well it sure is pretty.

113
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:45,500
This pink bowl
strikes your fancy?

114
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:46,625
I'll buy it for you.

115
00:07:46,708 --> 00:07:48,583
