116
00:07:48,666 --> 00:07:50,000
Oh. Don't be shy.

117
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:52,666
I'm not. But they say
everything comes at a price,

118
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,750
and it's the truth.

119
00:07:53,833 --> 00:07:54,666
[MASTER]
Oh...

120
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,750
