to a tasty meal right now?

123
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:03,041
[AOI]
What? Hm.

124
00:08:03,125 --> 00:08:04,375
[AOI gasps]

125
00:08:07,083 --> 00:08:09,250
These innards,
they're delicious!

126
00:08:09,333 --> 00:08:10,833
It's grilled offal.

127
00:08:10,916 --> 00:08:13,250
[AOI] Huh, I've never
had them like that.

128
00:08:13,333 --> 00:08:15,416
They really are great!

129
00:08:19,666 --> 00:08:21,041
So, did you order me

130
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:23,625
