137
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:40,541
[SUZURAN]
Excuse me, may I come in?

138
00:08:40,625 --> 00:08:41,541
Yes. Please.

139
00:08:41,625 --> 00:08:43,541
[door opens]

140
00:08:49,458 --> 00:08:52,000
It's been quite a while
since our last meeting,

141
00:08:52,083 --> 00:08:55,583
Master Innkeeper of Tenjin-ya.

142
00:08:55,666 --> 00:08:57,333
Aoi, meet one of

143
00:08:57,416 --> 00:09:00,541
the most popular
geishas in the capital, Suzuran.

144
00:09:00,625 --> 00:09:03,125
She's also
Akatsuki's younger sister.

145
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:04,500
What?

146
00:09:08,625 --> 00:09:11,791
Wait, the front desk guy?
She's related to him?

147
00:09:11,875 --> 00:09:14,833
Suzuran,
please meet Aoi Tsubaki,

148
00:09:14,916 --> 00:09:17,333
Shiro Tsubaki's granddaughter.

149
00:09:17,416 --> 00:09:19,666
Oh really, is that so?

150
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,291
Is he in the hidden realm
with you?

151
00:09:22,375 --> 00:09:24,166
Uh, my grandfather is--

152
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,208
Shiro isn't in
the hidden realm now.

153
00:09:26,291 --> 00:09:28,416
Aoi's the only Tsubaki here.

154
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,791
[SUZURAN]
I see.

155
00:09:29,875 --> 00:09:32,875
Well, I hope he visits soon,
it's been a long time.

156
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:39,125
I must tell you, Mistress Aoi.

157
00:09:39,208 --> 00:09:41,958
You resemble Shiro
a great deal.

158
00:09:42,041 --> 00:09:43,833
[gasps]

159
00:09:43,916 --> 00:09:45,791
[SUZURAN laughs]

160
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,375
Now, then, Suzuran,
it's been so long.

161
00:09:51,458 --> 00:09:54,208
I would love to hear you
play shamisen for us.

162
00:09:54,291 --> 00:09:55,875
[SUZURAN]
Of course.

163
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:59,708
[music plays]

164
00:10:08,833 --> 00:10:10,583
[music continues]

165
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,708
[door closes]

166
00:10:20,416 --> 00:10:22,541
Wow! Suzuran's
shamisen's great!

167
00:10:22,625 --> 00:10:24,125
She's very talented,

168
00:10:24,208 --> 00:10:27,416
and the offal hot pot
was incredible, too!

169
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,041
Thanks for treating me.

170
00:10:29,125 --> 00:10:31,708
Yes, you're quite welcome.

171
00:10:31,791 --> 00:10:34,250
How'd you like to go
get some dessert?

172
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:35,541
You bet!

173
00:10:36,708 --> 00:10:39,166
Honesty. I like it.

174
00:10:47,875 --> 00:10:51,375
[AOI] I feel like I'm being
watched by an <i>ayakashi.</i>

175
00:10:53,791 --> 00:10:55,166
[MAN 3C]
Keep it moving, lady!

176
00:11:02,916 --> 00:11:04,208
Uh!

177
00:11:05,583 --> 00:11:07,541
[AOI]
Where's the master?

178
00:11:15,583 --> 00:11:17,333
Ah! Ah!

179
00:11:17,416 --> 00:11:18,791
That hurt.

180
00:11:20,708 --> 00:11:22,583
[AOI]
An ice patch?

181
00:11:29,125 --> 00:11:30,458
[AOI gasps]

182
00:11:35,208 --> 00:11:36,291
[MAN 3D]
She's human.

183
00:11:36,375 --> 00:11:37,666
[MAN 3E]
A human girl!

184
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:38,833
[MAN 3F]
Looks tasty.

185
00:11:38,916 --> 00:11:42,000
