[AOI]
Whoa, awesome!

190
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:02,541
I didn't know this thing
packed so much wind power!

191
00:12:15,708 --> 00:12:17,416
Hey, come back!

192
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,625
[AOI grunts]

193
00:12:26,166 --> 00:12:27,375
