by <i>ayakashi</i> back there!

200
00:12:40,541 --> 00:12:42,708
Heh, I wish they had eaten you.

201
00:12:42,791 --> 00:12:46,333
You're just a human girl who has
no business with the master.

202
00:12:46,416 --> 00:12:49,000
He's far out of your league.

203
00:12:49,083 --> 00:12:51,000
So that's why you were spying.

204
00:12:51,083 --> 00:12:53,583
Uh! 'Scuse me?

205
00:12:53,666 --> 00:12:54,916
I know.

206
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:57,208
