today before we set sail.

207
00:12:57,291 --> 00:12:59,250
What? Go away.

208
00:12:59,333 --> 00:13:00,541
[ITTAN MOMEN 3A]
Hold it!

209
00:13:00,625 --> 00:13:02,375
[ITTAN MOMEN 3B]
Stop her!

210
00:13:03,916 --> 00:13:05,875
[AOI]
Is that Suzuran?

211
00:13:05,958 --> 00:13:07,708
Help me! Where's the master?

212
00:13:07,791 --> 00:13:09,666
[ITTAN MOMEN 3A]
She went down that street!

213
00:13:11,375 --> 00:13:12,625
[AOI]
Come on!

214
00:13:14,875 --> 00:13:16,458
[ITTAN MOMEN 3A]
Hey, where'd she go?

215
00:13:16,541 --> 00:13:17,500
[ITTAN MOMEN 3B]
That way!

216
00:13:17,583 --> 00:13:19,000
[ITTAN MOMEN 3A]
Dammit! Find her!

217
00:13:19,083 --> 00:13:20,666
[footsteps]

218
00:13:22,541 --> 00:13:23,958
[AOI sighs]

219
00:13:24,041 --> 00:13:26,791
Are you okay?
