224
00:13:34,458 --> 00:13:36,833
Those men who were
chasing after you just now,

225
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:39,416
they are the ittan-momen
from Yahata-ya.

226
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:40,833
What's that?

227
00:13:40,916 --> 00:13:42,791
A large and well-known
kimono shop.

228
00:13:42,875 --> 00:13:45,208
