229
00:13:45,291 --> 00:13:49,000
Suzuran, what made them
come after you?

230
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:51,375
[SUZURAN]
I was...

231
00:13:51,458 --> 00:13:53,458
I was just sold off.

232
00:13:55,291 --> 00:13:56,833
