the geisha house earlier,

235
00:14:01,041 --> 00:14:04,458
I was commanded
to marry into Yahata-ya.

236
00:14:05,458 --> 00:14:07,750
[SUZURAN] I heard they paid
an enormous sum for me.

237
00:14:07,833 --> 00:14:09,000
How awful!

238
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:10,708
