surprised to hear it.

239
00:14:10,791 --> 00:14:12,916
That man is a
low-life womanizer.

240
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,708
He's always harassed
the female staff

241
00:14:14,791 --> 00:14:16,208
at Tenjin-ya, too.

242
00:14:16,291 --> 00:14:18,625
