244
00:14:20,666 --> 00:14:22,541
[MASTER]
I see what's going on.

245
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:24,375
[SUZURAN]
Master, I'm so relieved!

246
00:14:24,458 --> 00:14:26,208
Uhm, I...

247
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,791
So young hostess,

248
00:14:37,875 --> 00:14:39,958
did you plan
to be back at Tenjin-ya

249
00:14:40,041 --> 00:14:41,166
